author: Clifford Atiyeh
title: 2018 Jaguar F-Pace: New Four-Cylinder and a Portfolio
text:
-With the MSRP of several Jaguar models now ringing in below the vaunted $50,000 mark, there’s more reason than ever to cross-shop British wares or at least notice their presence amid a sea of American, German, and Asian competitors. For the 2018 model year, the automaker’s top seller, the F-Pace, continues its pricing assault on the compact-SUV segment with a new base inline-four-cylinder engine, a new Portfolio trim, and extra safety features. READ MORE ››
